That's it.

434
00:33:39,019 --> 00:33:42,086
David, Richard.
It's gonna be, I think, all men.

435
00:33:42,604 --> 00:33:43,913
I think I can handle it.

436
00:33:44,141 --> 00:33:45,254
Good luck.

437
00:33:45,453 --> 00:33:46,762
John.

