00:34:44,412 --> 00:34:46,933
I thought your grandmother
lived in Miami.

446
00:34:47,453 --> 00:34:48,948
Well, you know...

447
00:34:50,878 --> 00:34:55,352
Well, we all thought she wasn't
gonna make it. It was like a miracle.

