464
00:36:59,552 --> 00:37:01,462
Where did you learn to cook so well?

465
00:37:03,458 --> 00:37:04,668
My mother.

466
00:37:04,834 --> 00:37:07,290
Seriously? I thought
you were gonna say you studied...

467
00:37:07,459 --> 00:37:09,849
